  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/9e6ed7b977a99a285e00b065e4fec6df.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicker game played at the bottom of the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The screen position can be adjusted up and down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Story-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A village chief is lost on the road after his village is destroyed by demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lord of the village gives him an order to open up a new frontier and cultivate the land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village chief's hell of endless cultivation begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Game Contents-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village headman accumulates pioneering power by clicking, chopping trees, smashing rocks, and hitting demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build buildings, increase your pioneering power, and open up uncharted lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use pioneering power at camps to increase your power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join new pioneers and increase your workforce.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/94bf6ba3df3bd766135ac22c56b3795c.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/9e6ed7b977a99a285e00b065e4fec6df.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicker game played at the bottom of the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The screen position can be adjusted up and down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Story-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A village chief is lost on the road after his village is destroyed by demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lord of the village gives him an order to open up a new frontier and cultivate the land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village chief's hell of endless cultivation begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Game Contents-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village headman accumulates pioneering power by clicking, chopping trees, smashing rocks, and hitting demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build buildings, increase your pioneering power, and open up uncharted lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use pioneering power at camps to increase your power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join new pioneers and increase your workforce.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/94bf6ba3df3bd766135ac22c56b3795c.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p>",
